name: Freljord佛雷尔卓德_T
description:
1）可作为单独的佛雷尔卓德的生成Lora，前几张都是无tag生成的，后面加了些人物的tag，推荐权重0.9左右。

It can be used as a separate Freljord generation Lora, the first few are generated without tags, followed by some characters' tags, and the recommended weight is about 0.9.

2）也可以作为画风增强器，最后一张是添加了lora的废墟场景，会增强“废墟”、“木板”、“石头”、“冰雪”的质感，推荐权重0.6左右。

It can also be used as a style enhancer, and the last one is a ruins scene with LoRa added, which will enhance the texture of "ruins", "boards", "stones", "ice and snow", and the recommended weight is about 0.6.
